  <description type="morphology">Plants 0.3–0.8 × 1–2 dm. Leaves: petiole 0.1–0.4 cm, base distinct, glabrous abaxially; blade elliptic, 0.5–1.5 × 0.2–0.45(–0.6) cm, margins often crenulate. Scapes 0.2–0.7(–1) dm. Flowers (2–)2.5–3 mm. Achenes 3.5–4 mm.</description>
